solution:
Drawing altitude $\overline{BD}$ splits $\triangle ABC$ into 30-60-90 triangle $ABD$ and 45-45-90 triangle $BCD$:

[asy]
import olympiad; size(200); import geometry; import graph; defaultpen(linewidth(0.8));
